-- UN Climate Talks Draft Text Calls for Greenhouse-Gas Emissions 2015 Peak
-- B y   K i m   C h i p m a n
-- 2010-12-08T16:43:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-08/un-climate-talks-draft-text-calls-for-greenhouse-gas-emissions-2015-peak.html
A call for greenhouse gas emissions
to peak in developed countries by 2015 is included in new draft
conclusions for United Nations climate talks in Cancun, Mexico.
The document was released by the UN Framework Convention on
Climate Change and gives options to ministers considering a text
to release at the end of the talks.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kim Chipman in Washington at 
 kchipman@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
